    "name": "Clinic Appointment System - Doctors API",
    "description": "Collection of Doctor module endpoints for the Clinic Appointment System.\n\n## Features\n- List all doctors with pagination and filtering\n- Get doctor details\n- Check doctor availability\n- Update doctor schedule\n\n## Base URL\nLocal: `http://localhost:3000`\n\n## Authentication\nMost endpoints will require JWT authentication (to be implemented).",
