        {
          "name": "Update Doctor Schedule",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"timeSlots\": [\n    {\n      \"startTime\": \"2025-10-15T09:00:00Z\",\n      \"endTime\": \"2025-10-15T09:30:00Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"startTime\": \"2025-10-15T09:30:00Z\",\n      \"endTime\": \"2025-10-15T10:00:00Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"startTime\": \"2025-10-15T10:00:00Z\",\n      \"endTime\": \"2025-10-15T10:30:00Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"startTime\": \"2025-10-15T10:30:00Z\",\n      \"endTime\": \"2025-10-15T11:00:00Z\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/doctors/{{doctorId}}/schedule",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["doctors", "{{doctorId}}", "schedule"]
            },
            "description": "Create or update a doctor's availability schedule.\n\n**Path Parameters:**\n- `id`: Doctor's user ID (UUID)\n\n**Request Body:**\n```json\n{\n  \"timeSlots\": [\n    {\n      \"startTime\": \"ISO 8601 datetime\",\n      \"endTime\": \"ISO 8601 datetime\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Business Rules:**\n- Only the doctor can update their own schedule\n- Each slot must be at least 15 minutes long\n- Slots cannot overlap\n- Cannot delete slots with active (BOOKED) appointments\n- Old slots without appointments will be soft-deleted\n\n**Authentication:**\nRequires authentication (to be implemented).\n\n**Response:**\nReturns created/updated/deleted counts and new time slots."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Success",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "PUT",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"timeSlots\": [\n    {\n      \"startTime\": \"2025-10-15T09:00:00Z\",\n      \"endTime\": \"2025-10-15T09:30:00Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"startTime\": \"2025-10-15T09:30:00Z\",\n      \"endTime\": \"2025-10-15T10:00:00Z\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
